IP Config Commands		
Action		Command
Shows IP address information		ipconfig
Shows detailed information		ipconfig /all
Renews IP address of all adapters		ipconfig /renew
Renews connection whose name starts with EL		ipconfig /renew EL*
Release all matching connections		ipconfig /release *Con*
Show information about all compartments		ipconfig /allcompartments
Show detailed information about all compartments		ipconfig /allcompartments /all
Display DNS Cache		ipconfig /displaydns
		
Ping the specified host until stopped		ping -t
		
		
Ping sweep		Â for /l %i in (1,1,254) do ping -n 1 -w 100 <first three octets of host network>.%i
